{"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"declarations","declarations":[{"languages":["occ"],"platforms":["iOS"],"tokens":[{"text":"- (","kind":"text"},{"text":"void","kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"c:v"},{"text":") ","kind":"text"},{"text":"setTargetCoordinate:","kind":"identifier"},{"text":"(","kind":"text"},{"text":"CLLocationCoordinate2D","kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"c:@S@CLLocationCoordinate2D"},{"text":") ","kind":"text"},{"text":"targetCoordinate","kind":"internalParam"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"animated:","kind":"identifier"},{"text":"(","kind":"text"},{"text":"BOOL","kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"c:@T@BOOL"},{"text":") ","kind":"text"},{"text":"animated","kind":"internalParam"},{"text":";","kind":"text"}]}]},{"kind":"parameters","parameters":[{"name":"targetCoordinate","content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The target coordinate to fit within the viewport."}]}]},{"name":"animated","content":[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"If ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"YES"},{"text":", the map animates to fit the target within the map","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"view. If ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"NO"},{"text":", the map fits the target instantaneously.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}]}]},{"content":[{"type":"heading","anchor":"discussion","text":"Discussion","level":2},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"By default, the target coordinate is set to an invalid coordinate, indicating","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"that there is no target. In course tracking mode, the target forms one of two","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"foci in the viewport, the other being the user location annotation. Typically,","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"the target is set to a destination or waypoint in a real-time navigation scene.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"As the user annotation moves toward the target, the map automatically zooms in","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"to fit both foci optimally within the viewport.","type":"text"}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"This method has no effect if the ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"userTrackingMode"},{"text":" property is set to a value","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"other than ","type":"text"},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNUserTrackingMode\/MLNUserTrackingModeFollowWithCourse","type":"reference","isActive":true},{"text":".","type":"text"}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"To specify a completion handler to execute after the animation finishes, use","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"the ","type":"text"},{"code":"-setTargetCoordinate:animated:completionHandler:","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" method.","type":"text"}]}],"kind":"content"}],"variants":[{"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"occ"}],"paths":["\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnmapview\/settargetcoordinate:animated:"]}],"metadata":{"remoteSource":{"fileName":"MLNMapView.h","url":"https:\/\/github.com\/maplibre\/maplibre-native\/blob\/main\/platform\/ios\/src\/MLNMapView.h#L775"},"title":"setTargetCoordinate:animated:","modules":[{"name":"MapLibre"}],"platforms":[{"unavailable":false,"deprecated":true,"beta":false}],"role":"symbol","symbolKind":"method","roleHeading":"Instance Method","externalID":"c:objc(cs)MLNMapView(im)setTargetCoordinate:animated:","fragments":[{"kind":"text","text":"- "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"setTargetCoordinate:animated:"}],"navigatorTitle":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"setTargetCoordinate:animated:"}]},"schemaVersion":{"patch":0,"minor":3,"major":0},"sections":[],"kind":"symbol","identifier":{"interfaceLanguage":"occ","url":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMapView\/setTargetCoordinate:animated:"},"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/org.swift.MyPr